more](https://buildspace.so/#more) it all begins online. on nights and
weekends. --------------------------------------------- this is where
you will take any idea you're excited about, figure out how to bring it
to life, and turn it into something that people give a shit about ---
alongside thousands of others. online + irl 10 hours/week completely
